.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢簡直係一股清流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都屌蝗<br />\n好值得鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a81664dd5f1abc36b6ca241cc57f5f63241616","tid":1072500,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"將來變做講「唔該同學」"},{"pid":"7a1b46c8bb00622547c884ae47ffe60dd42bed07","tid":1072500,"uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea46e1f6cef02e92030de231f4c6d026987d20d","tid":1072500,"uid":136645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T05:22:19.000Z","msg":"肯定私樓學童"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"連登已經痴哂線"}]}